message.content: Based on the provided volatility data, a possible payload of the initial exploit affecting the victim's bank account could be the file "sdra64.exe" located in \Device\HarddiskVolume1\WINDOWS\system32\. This file stands out as it is flagged as potentially malicious due to its location and naming convention. Further analysis of this file is recommended to determine its functionality and potential impact on the victim's system and bank account.
